## Introduction

Sexy stores inventory information in a cconfig database and
allows to control and change your environment using backends.

Thus you can always use the same tool to manage your inventory
and simply change the backend, if working in another environment.

## Installation

Get sexy from git ([gitweb](http://git.schottelius.org/?p=sexy;a=summary)):

    git clone git://git.schottelius.org/sexy


